OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain pushing eastwards, mostly light
OL,7,Fand patchy, but the odd heavier burst
OL,8,Fpossible in the west. Turning more
OL,9,Fshowery overnight, some drier and
OL,10,Fclearer spells by dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FBright spells and showers, the
OL,13,Fbest of the brightness for East
OL,14,FLothian and the eastern Borders during
OL,15,Fthe morning. The showers could be
OL,16,Fheavy, perhaps the odd rumble of
OL,17,Fthunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
